25#ifndef _ZFS_CTLDIR_H
26#define _ZFS_CTLDIR_H
27
28#include <sys/vnode.h>
29#include <sys/zfs_vfsops.h>
30#include <sys/zfs_znode.h>
31
32#ifdef __cplusplus
33extern "C" {
34#endif
35
36#define ZFS_CTLDIR_NAME ".zfs"
37
38#define zfs_has_ctldir(zdp) \
39 ((zdp)->z_id == (zdp)->z_zfsvfs->z_root && \
40 ((zdp)->z_zfsvfs->z_ctldir != NULL))
41#define zfs_show_ctldir(zdp) \
42 (zfs_has_ctldir(zdp) && \
43 ((zdp)->z_zfsvfs->z_show_ctldir))
44
45void zfsctl_create(zfsvfs_t *);
46void zfsctl_destroy(zfsvfs_t *);
47#ifdef __NetBSD__
48int zfsctl_loadvnode(vfs_t *, vnode_t *, const void *, size_t, const void **);
49int zfsctl_vptofh(vnode_t *, fid_t *, size_t *);
50int zfsctl_root(zfsvfs_t *, vnode_t **);
51int zfsctl_snapshot(zfsvfs_t *, vnode_t **);
52#else
53int zfsctl_root(zfsvfs_t *, int, vnode_t **);
54#endif
55void zfsctl_init(void);
56void zfsctl_fini(void);
57boolean_t zfsctl_is_node(vnode_t *);
58
59int zfsctl_rename_snapshot(const char *from, const char *to);
60int zfsctl_destroy_snapshot(const char *snapname, int force);
61int zfsctl_umount_snapshots(vfs_t *, int, cred_t *);
62
63int zfsctl_lookup_objset(vfs_t *vfsp, uint64_t objsetid, zfsvfs_t **zfsvfsp);
64
65#define ZFSCTL_INO_ROOT 0x1
66#define ZFSCTL_INO_SNAPDIR 0x2
67
68#ifdef __cplusplus
69}
70#endif
71
72#endif /* _ZFS_CTLDIR_H */
